# Part 3

## 1. Why do most children think education is boring?

I think one major reason is that traditional education is often too focused on memorization and exams. Many students spend a lot of time listening to teachers passively instead of participating actively, so classes can feel repetitive and stressful.

Another reason is that some subjects may seem disconnected from real life. If children cannot see how knowledge is useful in daily life, they may lose interest quickly. I think education becomes much more interesting when students can learn through experiments, discussions, or practical activities.

### 中文：

我觉得一个主要原因是传统教育太强调记忆和考试。很多学生只是被动听老师讲课，而不是主动参与，所以课堂容易变得重复而有压力。

另一个原因是，有些学科看起来和现实生活联系不大。如果孩子无法理解知识在生活中的实际用途，他们就会很快失去兴趣。我觉得如果能通过实验、讨论或者实践活动学习，教育会更有趣。

---

## 2. Why aren't young people willing to listen to the experiences of older people?

I think many young people believe that society is changing very quickly, especially because of technology and the internet. As a result, they may feel that older generations’ experiences are outdated or less relevant to modern life.

Besides that, young people usually want to make their own decisions and learn from personal experience instead of simply following advice from others. However, I still think older people’s experiences are valuable because they can help younger generations avoid unnecessary mistakes.

### 中文：

我觉得很多年轻人认为社会变化太快了，尤其是在科技和互联网快速发展的背景下，所以他们可能会觉得老一辈的经验已经不太适用于现代生活。

此外，年轻人通常更希望自己做决定，并通过亲身经历去学习，而不是单纯听从别人的建议。不过我仍然认为老年人的经验很有价值，因为它能帮助年轻人避免很多不必要的错误。

---

## 3. What can people do when they feel bored?

When people feel bored, I think the best thing is to try something new. For example, they can learn a new skill, exercise, travel, or spend time with friends. New experiences usually help people feel more energetic and motivated.

Personally, when I feel bored, I often watch interesting videos, listen to music, or study something related to AI and technology because learning new things makes me feel productive and excited again.

### 中文：

当人们感到无聊时，我觉得最好的办法是尝试一些新事物。比如学习新技能、运动、旅行，或者和朋友一起出去玩。新的体验通常会让人重新变得有活力。

就我个人而言，当我感到无聊时，我通常会看一些有趣的视频、听音乐，或者学习人工智能和科技相关的内容，因为学习新东西会让我重新感到充实和兴奋。
